        <h3 class="article__heading">Outcome</h3>

        <p>This workshop was well-received, and my teammates really appreciated the role playing exercises and time dedicated to acknowledging and working through difficult conversations. They liked taking on the client‚Äôs perspective as well as their own, for it helped them see the scenario from both sides. I think the best takeaway from this day was that newer team members said they were exposed to scenarios and difficult conversations that they didn‚Äôt realize were common. They said they felt more prepared going into client engagements, knowing what to look out for and how to recognize and address potential issues before they escalated.</p>

